node.text:
I often wonder if there is any link to the new monitoring systems being created.... you see bio microchipping in sweden, Bill Gates/microsoft and the patent filing WO 2020/060606 which you have to read the further description details to see what kinds of bio data they want to collect and the means... (which seems unlimited) and its tie to electronic currency.... and his other Biotech investments.... and of course...

Then how do you lead the general population to allow such a thing to believe it's for the greater good.... a virus... perhaps?  this is for discussion.... but considering the things we have seen in the last 6 months... and the push for total Gov control by some political, socialism, marxists elements... combined with the decimation of middle class jobs by a virus that's seems to have been predicted just a year ago...by many of the same people.. the mass exodus of CEOs in 2019,.... and so on. 

if we could make a list of all major gov policy changes since 9/11... and tech.. what kind of big picture would we get from it?  does it point to a direction?  is it possible that being inundated with information is also a way to create and control perception?  all just food for thought.
